data.name: IntroPart1
data.value: Hello! I'm Morten. I'm a software developer with a passion for data visualisation. I have a keen interest in the latest developments in web frameworks and building powerful web applications.

data.name: IntroPart2
data.value: I have a background in Theoretical Physics and I have a particular interest in Quantum Computing.

data.name: FractalChaosTextLong
data.value: The chaos game is a game of very simple rules that produces remarkable fractal structures. This post explores a variety of different structures and the code used to generate them.

data.name: MengerTextLong
data.value: The Menger sponge is a three-dimensional fractal curve that exhibits infinite surface area and zero volume. This shows the POV-Ray code to render this mathematical structure

data.name: MengerTextShort
data.value: The Menger sponge is a three-dimensional fractal curve with infinite surface area
